data.description: Experience the epitome of eco-luxury living at Piedra Vista in NE ABQ! This tranquil foothills retreat is equipped with solar, (2) 3.5-ton 13 SEER / 40,000-140,000 BTU heating and cooling units, as well as two backup gas furnaces. Revel in the breathtaking views of Albuquerque city lights, ''Three Sisters,'' and majestic Mt. Taylor. Indulge in the opulence of a 5-piece primary bath featuring an expansive jacuzzi tub. The recently remodeled kitchen showcases exquisite granite counters and beautifully crafted solid wood countertops. This home offers multiple living areas, a cozy gas log fireplace, & a convenient wet bar. Radiant, welcoming, &designed for efficiency, this home embodies modern comfort. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule your private showing today!!
